<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>We should optionally allow the client to request a gzipped response from the GD client library.  Architecture of this has to be investigated (service object, http client, etc).</p>

<p>In order to support getting a gzipped response, 'gzip' needs to be in the user-agent, but an accept-encoding header is also required to enable gzip.</p>

    </div>
